That is what | am saying.

1533
01:57:08,696 --> 01:57:10,630
She can become
orphan if you do haste.

1534
01:57:10,731 --> 01:57:12,460
Sita won't become an orphan.

1535
01:57:12,667 --> 01:57:16,126
| will ruin that
scoundrel's village.

1536
01:57:16,236 --> 01:57:17,294
| will destroy it.

1537
01:57:19,040 --> 01:57:22,772
You will tarnish Sita's image.

1538
01:57:23,544 --> 01:57:24,602
Shall | say something else?

1539
01:57:25,112 --> 01:57:27,308
You will make her a widow?

1540
01:57:29,483 --> 01:57:30,541
Will that be fine?

1541
01:57:31,519 --> 01:57:32,543
Listen.

1542
01:57:32,720 --> 01:57:36,452
After your decision,
this won't stop.

1543
01:57:37,191 --> 01:57:39,455
Go. Take your revenge.

1544
01:57:42,763 --> 01:57:45,664
Brute.

1545
01:57:46,767 --> 01:57:48,326
Brute.

1546
01:57:48,469 --> 01:57:49,493
Wicked man.

1547
01:57:49,603 --> 01:57:50,729
Brute.

1548
01:57:52,807 --> 01:57:55,799
Brute. Brute. Brute.

1549
01:57:56,110 --> 01:57:57,339
Brute.

1550
01:57:59,079 --> 01:58:03,744
Brute. Brute. Brute.

1551
01:58:04,685 --> 01:58:05,709
Brother.

1552
01:58:20,868 --> 01:58:23,166
Why did they send you here?

1553
01:58:23,771 --> 01:58:26,206
Have they sent you to your
brother's house forever?

1554
01:58:34,448 --> 01:58:36,507
Dhanraj has sent this
letter with your sister.

1555
01:58:48,329 --> 01:58:49,387
Read it out.

1556
01:58:53,768 --> 01:58:56,100
"Suraj, is your sister's life dear..

1557
01:58:56,203 --> 01:58:57,693
..or the villagers'
life dear to you."

1558
01:58:57,805 --> 01:58:59,705
"It's time to decide.”

1559
01:59:00,474 --> 01:59:03,307
"This time there was a lot of
corruption in the election.”

1560
01:59:03,811 --> 01:59:06,644
"That's why | am filing a
case to cancel the election.”

1561
01:59:07,148 --> 01:59:10,482
"At the hearing you will
have to testify in my favor."

1562
01:59:10,751 --> 01:59:11,809
"The election will be held again."

1563
01:59:12,320 --> 01:59:13,810
"You won't lock horns with me."

1564
01:59:14,388 --> 01:59:17,688
"If you do that, your
sister's life will become hell."

1565
01:59:34,775 --> 01:59:36,709
You will blame me?

1566
01:59:37,611 --> 01:59:42,549
No. It's not right to put your
family at stake to save your honor.

1567
01:59:43,717 --> 01:59:45,446
It's a crime to
beat a hapless woman.

1568
01:59:46,387 --> 01:59:49,823
Beating your brother's wife
is not a decent thing to do.

1569
01:59:52,827 --> 01:59:56,388
It is better that you forget the
mistake that you did in your haste..

1570
01:59:57,264 --> 01:59:59,528
..Apologize to Suraj
and bring Sita home.

1571
02:00:03,938 --> 02:00:05,702
Today, you have made
me realize my mistake.

1572
02:00:06,707 --> 02:00:10,405
| should apologize to
Suraj and bring Sita back.

1573
02:00:10,844 --> 02:00:13,336
| think it is best.

1574
02:00:14,582 --> 02:00:16,949
Will you go or shall | go?

1575
02:00:17,518 --> 02:00:20,647
Brother, your
decision has made me happy.

1576
02:00:21,489 --> 02:00:23,457
| was sure you will listen to me.

1577
02:00:25,526 --> 02:00:28,518
| am so reputed.

1578
02:00:28,862 --> 02:00:31,695
And you want to tarnish my image.

1579
02:00:31,966 --> 02:00:33,229
If you utter another word..
- Sir.

1580
02:00:33,334 --> 02:00:34,392
Sir.
- What happened?

1581
02:00:34,868 --> 02:00:38,304
Two men and a eunuch
have come to meet you.

1582
02:00:44,611 --> 02:00:47,478
All three of you are
Suraj's friends, right?

1583
02:00:47,581 --> 02:00:49,948
Yes, sir. We have
come here as Hanuman.

1584
02:00:50,250 --> 02:00:51,308
As messengers?

1585
02:00:51,418 --> 02:00:52,886
Hanuman had brought a ring.

1586
02:00:53,387 --> 02:00:55,253
We have brought
this letter. Take it.

1587
02:00:56,390 --> 02:00:57,619
Balram.
- Yes, sir.

1588
02:00:57,725 --> 02:00:59,557
Look after the guests.
- Okay, sir.

1589
02:01:00,261 --> 02:01:01,729
Are we guests for two to three days?

1590
02:01:01,829 --> 02:01:02,853
Shut up, eunuch. Come on.

1591
02:01:04,264 --> 02:01:05,288
Read it.

1592
02:01:10,404 --> 02:01:12,236
Read it quickly.
-Yes.

1593
02:01:12,339 --> 02:01:15,741
"Dhanraj, | have not
decided to serve people.."

1594
02:01:15,843 --> 02:01:17,242
"..to hear false praises like you."

1595
02:01:17,411 --> 02:01:19,470
"For the wellbeing
of Rajoli's workers.."

1596
02:01:19,580 --> 02:01:22,345
"..if Sita leads a
miserable life, | don't mind."

1597
02:01:22,450 --> 02:01:24,612
"You can't do anything worse."

1598
02:01:24,818 --> 02:01:29,278
"But to save people from
a greedy man like you.."

1599
02:01:29,390 --> 02:01:31,757
.1 will lock horns
with you all my life."

1600
02:01:32,059 --> 02:01:33,322
Shut up.

1601
02:01:34,529 --> 02:01:36,258
Why are you beating me?

1602
02:01:36,463 --> 02:01:38,295
| was reading out whatever he wrote.

1603
02:01:47,575 --> 02:01:48,599
Why did you come here?

1604
02:01:49,643 --> 02:01:52,704
To see whether
Dhanraj is alive or dead?

1605
02:01:53,547 --> 02:01:56,380
That insolent fellow
made an ordinary man win..

1606
02:01:56,483 --> 02:01:58,383
..just to humiliate me.

1607
02:01:58,485 --> 02:01:59,543
Don't you feel ashamed?

1608
02:01:59,954 --> 02:02:01,319
Go and die somewhere.

1609
02:02:02,322 --> 02:02:04,984
We won't rest in peace
until we don't take revenge.

1610
02:02:05,359 --> 02:02:06,417
| will take revenge.

1611
02:02:06,593 --> 02:02:10,291
| will burn Rajoli the way |
am burning with rage right now.

1612
02:02:10,398 --> 02:02:12,890
1 will Kill all
those who helped him.

1613
02:02:13,534 --> 02:02:16,629
Only after | kill Suraj,
who snatched my post..

1614
02:02:16,804 --> 02:02:18,568
..will anything be
cooked in my house.

1615
02:02:18,672 --> 02:02:20,504
And | will rest in peace.

1616
02:02:20,608 --> 02:02:21,803
Tell me. What do we have to do?

1617
02:02:22,977 --> 02:02:25,912
A fair is going to be held in
their village's Goddess Kali temple.

1618
02:02:26,647 --> 02:02:29,514
Suraj will surely come
to worship Goddess Kali.

1619
02:02:29,850 --> 02:02:33,013
There will be havoc.

1620
02:02:33,454 --> 02:02:38,415
In that havoc Banwari along
with his cronies will shoot Suraj.

1621
02:02:38,993 --> 02:02:40,757
There won't be any witness.

1622
02:03:00,748 --> 02:03:02,375
| was waiting since a long time.

1623
02:03:04,018 --> 02:03:06,749
It's not good for us to meet.

1624
02:03:08,155 --> 02:03:10,487
| couldn't send the
message through someone.

1625
02:03:11,725 --> 02:03:12,954
That's why | came.

1626
02:03:16,630 --> 02:03:20,362
He plans to wreak
havoc in the village.

1627
02:03:20,634 --> 02:03:21,692
| suspected this.

1628
02:03:21,802 --> 02:03:24,499
He will kill you during the riot.

1629
02:03:27,174 --> 02:03:28,938
Beatings will happen suddenly.

1630
02:03:29,543 --> 02:03:32,604
As far as possible, stay
away from the quarrel.

1631
02:03:33,080 --> 02:03:37,677
You have come to tell me this.
Shall | believe you?

1632
02:03:43,557 --> 02:03:46,925
He has gone crazy
because of his defeat.

1633
02:03:47,895 --> 02:03:49,795
| don't know what he will do
in his desire for revenge.

1634
02:03:51,098 --> 02:03:52,429
| am afraid..

1635
02:03:54,068 --> 02:03:55,763
..his life might be in danger.

1636
02:03:57,572 --> 02:04:00,542
| can't even dream of
seeing you as a widow.

1637
02:04:02,443 --> 02:04:03,706
| am not afraid for myself.

1638
02:04:04,779 --> 02:04:06,508
| am afraid for my unborn child.

1639
02:04:07,548 --> 02:04:08,947
| don't want people
to taunt him saying..

1640
02:04:09,050 --> 02:04:10,484
..he caused his father's death.

1641
02:04:14,655 --> 02:04:15,713
Congratulations.

1642
02:04:17,525 --> 02:04:18,583
Sita?

1643
02:04:20,094 --> 02:04:22,654
Let your husband's anger abate.

1644
02:04:22,963 --> 02:04:25,193
| will meet him and take a decision.

1645
02:04:50,691 --> 02:04:53,126
You know it's a sin not to
control your desires, don't you?

1646
02:04:54,061 --> 02:04:55,153
It's written in the Vedas.

1647
02:04:55,663 --> 02:04:57,097
But the man who has come here..

1648
02:04:57,198 --> 02:05:00,168
..people's favorite
leader Suraj Prakash..

1649
02:05:00,901 --> 02:05:06,237
..Vedas, religion or
justice nothing will stop him.

1650
02:05:08,976 --> 02:05:10,944
Earlier they would
meet outside the village.

1651
02:05:11,045 --> 02:05:12,570
Now, they are
meeting in the village.

1652
02:05:13,247 --> 02:05:14,806
Tomorrow they might
meet in the house.

1653
02:05:15,216 --> 02:05:18,117
Why? They might even
meet in my bedroom.

1654
02:05:18,753 --> 02:05:19,948
Don't say anything to him.

1655
02:05:20,120 --> 02:05:23,579
He is hapless people's God.

1656
02:05:23,791 --> 02:05:25,088
Helpless people's friend.

1657
02:05:25,292 --> 02:05:26,851
Farmers' well-wisher.

1658
02:05:27,094 --> 02:05:29,028
Rajoli's don.

1659
02:05:30,831 --> 02:05:32,799
He has the right to do anything.

1660
02:05:34,635 --> 02:05:35,966
Listen. What are you saying?

1661
02:05:36,070 --> 02:05:37,868
Shut up, shameless woman.

1662
02:05:41,041 --> 02:05:43,976
If you love him, why don't
you elope with him? - Dhanraj.

1663
02:05:44,211 --> 02:05:46,737
It's not a decent thing to humiliate
your wife in front of everyone.

1664
02:05:47,081 --> 02:05:50,210
She is my wife. And your mistress.

1665
02:05:50,318 --> 02:05:51,581
You..

1666
02:05:51,919 --> 02:05:53,910
Leave him. Leave him.

1667
02:05:58,559 --> 02:05:59,720
Go away.

1668
02:06:02,029 --> 02:06:03,861
It's an old proverb
that wife doesn't cross..

1669
02:06:03,965 --> 02:06:06,024
..the line drawn by her husband.

1670
02:06:06,300 --> 02:06:10,897
But he is a man who
listens to his lover.

1671
02:06:11,071 --> 02:06:13,165
Why are you talking like that?

1672
02:06:13,240 --> 02:06:17,006
| came here to beg for your life.

1673
02:06:17,578 --> 02:06:21,947
You are Kalyug's Savitri and
he is Yamraj (Lord of death).

1674
02:06:22,049 --> 02:06:24,074
You have come to
save my life from him.

1675
02:06:24,184 --> 02:06:25,549
Whom are you fooling?

1676
02:06:26,820 --> 02:06:29,084
Dhanraj, if you want to take
revenge from me, go ahead.

1677
02:06:29,190 --> 02:06:30,919
Don't blame an innocent woman.

1678
02:06:33,093 --> 02:06:36,028
| don't have the strength
to take revenge from you.

1679
02:06:36,597 --> 02:06:38,759
You are people's God.

1680
02:06:41,635 --> 02:06:43,899
If | speak against
you in front of them..

1681
02:06:44,705 --> 02:06:46,002
..they will hack me to death.

1682
02:06:46,373 --> 02:06:49,866
If this had happened in
my honorable village..

1683
02:06:49,977 --> 02:06:51,240
..people would have
chopped you into pieces..

1684
02:06:51,345 --> 02:06:53,245
..and thrown your
bits to dogs. But here..

1685
02:06:54,815 --> 02:06:56,078
..people are watching the spectacle.

1686
02:06:57,050 --> 02:06:59,951
If | seek justice, people will say..

1687
02:07:00,054 --> 02:07:02,785
"It is not our man's fault.
Your wife is at fault.”

1688
02:07:02,924 --> 02:07:05,222
Our village also has some rules.

1689
02:07:05,759 --> 02:07:08,319
We are not like those who
silently watch the spectacle..

1690
02:07:08,629 --> 02:07:11,291
..if a man casts lustful eyes
on a woman from another village.

1691
02:07:11,799 --> 02:07:14,131
We will pelt stones at him
and break his hands and feet.

1692
02:07:23,911 --> 02:07:25,345
Leave him. Leave him.

1693
02:07:25,646 --> 02:07:28,308
Don't beat him. Don't
beat him. Don't beat him.

1694
02:07:28,415 --> 02:07:29,974
- Beat me.

1695
02:07:30,217 --> 02:07:31,275
Shameless.

1696
02:07:31,886 --> 02:07:34,651
You are saving him in front of me.

1697
02:07:34,755 --> 02:07:35,813
Dhanraj.

1698
02:07:36,356 --> 02:07:38,882
She is pregnant.
Don't beat her brutally.

1699
02:07:39,860 --> 02:07:41,988
Who knows whether
it's my child or his?

1700
02:07:42,096 --> 02:07:43,154
Dhanraj.

1701
02:11:25,453 --> 02:11:26,477
Veena.

1702
02:11:30,991 --> 02:11:32,015
No. Don't touch me.

1703
02:11:40,200 --> 02:11:42,362
Listen.
- Veena. Veena.

1704
02:11:54,281 --> 02:11:55,339
Veena.

1705
02:11:56,116 --> 02:11:57,140
Forgive me.

1706
02:11:58,019 --> 02:12:01,512
Due to my ego | got
separated from all my loved ones.

1707
02:12:02,256 --> 02:12:07,217
After hearing my husband
say that my character is bad..

1708
02:12:08,195 --> 02:12:09,594
..instead of living..

1709
02:12:11,565 --> 02:12:13,533
..it is better that | die.

1710
02:12:14,702 --> 02:12:16,431
Veena. Veena.

1711
02:12:41,328 --> 02:12:42,352
Look.

1712
02:12:43,364 --> 02:12:45,059
Forget old enmity.

1713
02:12:45,500 --> 02:12:48,231
And bring Sita home. Yes.

1714
02:12:49,170 --> 02:12:51,195
Forget your differences.

1715
02:12:52,206 --> 02:12:53,537
And lead a happy life.

1716
02:13:10,324 --> 02:13:12,691
Wherever you go..

1717
02:13:14,361 --> 02:13:15,988
..as a milestone..

1718
02:13:18,432 --> 02:13:20,196
..my chaste soul..

1719
02:13:21,135 --> 02:13:29,135
"This life is perishable."

1720
02:13:31,211 --> 02:13:34,211
"Those who are born, they die."

